{"tid":1060932,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傑志泰迪去過土耳其無得去支那作客富力","createTime":"2019-03-14T04:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T13:46:23.000Z","uid":37528,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0e369c2b778a337f1bee555615643722ca67acdc","tid":1060932,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T04:58:25.000Z","msg":"傑志將於周六的港超聯賽事作客富力，惟陣中克羅地亞籍外援泰迪未能成功申請中國簽證，或無緣出賽，令傑志兵源受影響。總監兼總教練朱志光認為，目前以延期作賽最為合理。<br />\n<br />\n富力自上季起獲准使用位於中國廣州的燕子崗體育場作主場，而非在香港境內，今次終於迎來問題。傑志會長伍健昨於社交網站表示，泰迪未能取得中國簽證，皆因他曾去過土耳其。土耳其最近因為新疆問題而「傷害中國人民感情」，料是泰迪未能取得簽證的原因。<br />\n<br />\n主角泰迪今晨沒有出席球隊操練，朱志光解釋：「免得他太長時間沒有比賽，所以今晚他會踢預備組。」朱志光亦指，若泰迪最終未能上陣，不只是對傑志不公，而是對聯賽其他球隊也欠公道，「萬一傑志失分，也會影響到其他爭標球隊。不只是泰迪，不論是正選或後備，只要有一位球員未能上陣，也是不公平。」<br />\n<br />\n朱志光指，目前仍等待富力與足總解決事件，但認為改於香港境內其他球場比賽亦不恰當，「這樣做的話，對已作客富力的球隊亦不公平。」他認為暫時最理想的做法是球賽延期，更表示：「我去年才到過土耳其，最佳教練的禮物是機票嘛。」<br />\n<br />\n支那你使唔使咁撚驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「傷害中國人民感情」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cfce06eba18030b207b55a8ad6a6d6b75cdb034","tid":1060932,"uid":997,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:00:26.000Z","msg":"支那真係好撚垃圾"},{"pid":"ddf55cb6b7e20817850ebc59605de857bac335d0","tid":1060932,"uid":21275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:01:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"928bc86d5836923b5b79feb0ce40d267d26aeb97","tid":1060932,"uid":10795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:03:58.000Z","msg":"畜力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3682f712fbd2859606fdb58c11a0fd76c1ad65","tid":1060932,"uid":75406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:29:18.000Z","msg":"又話唔好將體育政治化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249e2e11a6bdc14189ed03634758e70413066acf","tid":1060932,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:30:12.000Z","msg":"罷踼啦"},{"pid":"986fca495aca904bb1893e030efebff0610d879e","tid":1060932,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:31:10.000Z","msg":"足球還足球"},{"pid":"9a682201470fc41b0c0a06c2997cd17dfb437911","tid":1060932,"uid":37528,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"249e2e11a6bdc14189ed03634758e70413066acf","tid":1060932,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:30:12.000Z","msg":"罷踼啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T12:25:36.000Z","msg":"應該咁多隊一齊杯9佢啦，當初俾隊支那球隊踢港超已經好火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c7cf94140f537720fab0d3aea48552d02c61ea","tid":1060932,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T12:26:42.000Z","msg":"仲有，亞冠外隊作客果陣又唔見支那夠膽咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf38fe6d4311f08900a57a5608082142f31f52d7","tid":1060932,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T13:25:53.000Z","msg":"簽證問題已解決"},{"pid":"f23b38f304a363dc3c001f60441d7ce6901bc117","tid":1060932,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T13:46:23.000Z","msg":"朱蛇都去過土2旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能都係鄂圖曼間諜嚟<br />\nBan埋朱蛇就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}